<h1>Activation Failed</h1>

<div
  style="
    background: #f8d7da;
    border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
    border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  "
>
  <p style="color: #721c24; margin: 0">
    <strong>❌ Error:</strong> <%= error %>
  </p>
</div>

<div
  style="
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  "
>
  <h2 style="color: #333; margin-top: 0">What happened?</h2>
  <ul style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8">
    <li>The activation link may have expired (links expire after 24 hours)</li>
    <li>The link may have already been used</li>
    <li>The link may be invalid or corrupted</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div
  style="
    background: #fff3cd;
    border: 1px solid #ffc107;
    border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  "
>
  <p style="color: #856404; margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem">
    <strong>💡 What to do:</strong> Contact your administrator to request a new
    activation link.
  </p>
</div>

<div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem">
  <a
    href="/"
    style="
      display: inline-block;
      background: #667eea;
      color: white;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    "
  >
    ← Back to Home
  </a>
  <a
    href="/auth/login"
    style="
      display: inline-block;
      background: #764ba2;
      color: white;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    "
  >
    Go to Login
  </a>
</div>
